  "instructions": [
    "Bring a pot of water to boil and cook spaghetti according to package instructions.",
    "Meanwhile, in a small bowl, mix low sodium soy sauce with gochujang until well combined.",
    "Heat oil in a wok or large skillet over medium-high heat. Add julienned watermelon radish, ginger, green onions, and the sauce mixture. Stir-fry for about 2 minutes.",
    "Add cooked spaghetti to the stir-fry and toss together to coat evenly with sauce. Remove from heat immediately to avoid overcooking.",
    "Stir in tahini until fully incorporated and serve."
